---
import ProfileSection from "../components/ProfileSection.astro";
---

<ProfileSection title="Work Experience">
  <div>
    <h3>
      Independent Consultant / KDDI DIGITAL GATE
      <span class="duration">Apr 2022 - Present</span>
    </h3>
    <ul>
      <li>
        Serve as the technical lead for new business incubation, guiding PoC
        ideation, solution architecture, implementation, verification, and
        launch for enterprise clients.
      </li>
      <li>
        Build TypeScript/React frontends and serverless backends (Hono on AWS
        Lambda, Fargate, EC2, DynamoDB; Azure App Service/Cosmos DB) while
        coaching teams on internal capability building and cloud governance.
      </li>
      <li>
        Introduce Scrum practices, facilitate cross-company squads, and provide
        AI/LLM technology research to accelerate decision making.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h3>
      Internet Initiative Japan Inc. (IIJ)
      <span class="duration">Apr 2013 - Dec 2020</span>
    </h3>
    <p>
      Led architecture, development, and operations for the IIJ GIO domestic
      cloud platform across multiple generations, covering frontend, backend,
      virtualization, network, and internal CI/CD infrastructure.
    </p>

    <div class="project">
      <h4>IIJ GIO Hosting Package Control Panel (2013 - 2014)</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Built and operated a new control panel and orchestration layer for the
          public cloud service, owning specification design, host operations,
          and on-call response.
        </li>
        <li>
          Established company-wide CI/CD tooling and rolled it out to improve
          delivery quality and speed within the project.
        </li>
        <li>Stack: JavaScript, Backbone.js, Ruby on Rails, MySQL, Linux/Xen.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="project">
      <h4>IIJ GIO Infrastructure P2 (2014 - 2019)</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Co-led the design of a refreshed KVM-based public cloud, producing UI
          and orchestration specifications and delivering the management console
          and automation services end-to-end.
        </li>
        <li>
          Integrated internal systems, negotiated network interfaces, designed
          network components, fortified CI/CD platforms, and defined operations
          and test plans for an 8-person squad.
        </li>
        <li>
          Stack: JavaScript/CoffeeScript, Backbone.js/Marionette, Ruby on Rails,
          MySQL, Linux/KVM+QEMU.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="project">
      <h4>IIJ GIO Infrastructure P2 Gen.2 (2019 - 2020)</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Served as development lead for the next-generation unified cloud,
          driving service ideation, target architecture, frontend delivery,
          operation and test design, and integration with corporate systems for
          a 12-person team.
        </li>
        <li>
          Introduced Scrum, led the rollout, and mentored teams to institutionalize agile development.
        </li>
        <li>Stack: JavaScript, Python/Flask, Java/Spring, PostgreSQL, VMware.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</ProfileSection>

<style>
  .duration {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: normal;
  }

  .project {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .project h4 {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
</style>
